<reggrp_short_dscr>:
Pipeline configuration indexed per port.
------------------------------
<reggrp_public_text>:
The parameters in this register group controls the behavior of statistic and policing per port and per action.

The register group is - by default - indexed by port number.
However VCAP IS2 action may change the index (PORT_PT_CTRL_IDX) using ACL_RT_MODE=1 and ACL_MAC action fields.
This is useful for Up-MEP SAT flows, where a VCAP IS2 rule+action can be configured to have the SAT frames use a PORT_PT_CTRL_IDX value which selects a PORT_PT_CTRL configuration with PVOE_DIS=1 and PSTAT_DIS=1, thus reflecting a behavior where SAT frames are not processed by the port MEP nor being counted in port statistics.
------------------------------
