------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Policer threshold size (a.ka. burst capacity). Unit is 2048 bytes
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0: Threshold = 0 bytes (no burst allowed)
1: Threshold = 2048 bytes
n: Threshold = n x 2048 bytes
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Specify rate in steps of configured granularity.

The rate granularity is configured in TIMESCALE_VAL.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0: Disable leak. For THRES_VAL = 0 bucket is always closed. For THRES_VAL > 0, the configured burst size is available.
1: 1 * granularity
2: 2 * granularity
...
max_value-1: (max_value-1)*granularity
max_value: Disable leaky bucket (always open)
